tool_description: Returns list of HTTP, HTTPS, SOCKS4, SOCKS5 proxies. Checks proxies each minute. Finds more than 7000 working proxies from multiple sources.
name: Proxy List
title: Proxy List

api_list.name: /proxy/get
api_list.description: Returns the list of proxies based on the given parameters. The list is updated every 1 minute. API returns only working at the time of check proxies.

optional_parameters.name: type
optional_parameters.description: Possible values: http, https, socks4, socks5

optional_parameters.name: country
optional_parameters.description: Use country code to filter data by country. Please check https://www.nationsonline.org/oneworld/country_code_list.htm for more information about country codes.

api_list.name: /proxy/health
api_list.description: ReturnS the health status of the API. Also return last time the proxies check was completed. Time is in UTC.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://proxy-list2.p.rapidapi.com/proxy/health"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "proxy-list2.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
